raw_data.title: Clerical
raw_data.description: Administrative assistant able to perform a number of secretarial and administrative duties. Able to provide human resources, project support, financial assistance, invoicing, and marketing processes. Can communicate with clients, employees, and other individuals to answer questions, disseminate or explain information, and address issues through the proper channels.

raw_data.title: Technician
raw_data.description: Technician to provide project support for fieldwork, material testing, and construction administration. Performs field work and technical analysis of systems and drafts necessary reports. Capable of taking all necessary measurements and photographic documentation for engineers to analyze. Able to work under minimal supervision once fully trained.

raw_data.title: AutoCad Drafter
raw_data.description: Technical drawing drafter able to provide engineering or technical drawings in a digital format, most likely using AutoCad or equivalent. Uses computer aided design equipment to provide support to senior management in preparing layouts, drawings, sketches, and diagrams. Capable of making simple design decisions but refers most questions/issues to engineers and/or supervisors. Solid understanding of drafting techniques and familiarity with facility engineering terminology.

raw_data.title: Lead Technician
raw_data.description: Technician to provide oversight of other technicians during fieldwork and facility projects; able to provide construction or subcontractor oversight. Performs field work and technical analysis of systems and drafts necessary reports. Oversees tasks such as: field observation and documentation of facility systems; construction administration and site visits; and quality control/assurance.

raw_data.title: Staff Engineer
raw_data.description: Degreed engineer capable of providing basic engineering drawings, calculations, project manuals, field measurements, and engineering solutions. Duties include engineering fieldwork (site measurements, photography, documenting damage), research, computer aided drafting/design, dictating reports, making cost estimates, performing presentations, conducting site visits during construction, materials testing, and maintaining equipment. Uses computer aided design equipment to provide support to senior management in preparing layouts, drawings, sketches, and diagrams. Thorough understanding of engineering principals, construction techniques, and engineering terminology.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: Associates Degree equal to two years relevant experience.

labor_categories.years_experience: Associates Degree equal to two years relevant experience.

raw_data.title: Senior Engineer
raw_data.description: A fully competent, licensed engineer able to oversee projects and act as project manager of engineering work. Capable of technical engineering work to include studies and assessments, engineering drawings and calculations, project manuals, field measurements, and engineering solutions to a wide array of Facility issues.  Serves as the project manager for design projects. Provides oversight to other technical staff and able to work independently. Capable of performing all duties of the Staff Engineer.

raw_data.title: Principal Engineer
raw_data.description: A fully competent, licensed engineer and highly technical expert able to provide both engineering and project management support to the entire client-base. Has a vested interest in the success of the firm as an owner in the corporation. Capable of technical engineering work to include studies and assessments, engineering drawings and calculations, project manuals, field measurements, and engineering solutions to a wide array of Facility issues.  Serves as the project manager for design projects. Provides oversight to other technical staff and able to work independently. Able to perform all duties of the Senior Engineer.

raw_data.title: Chief Engineer
raw_data.description: A fully competent, licensed engineer and Principal-in-Charge of all engineering and technical work completed within the company. An experienced and highly technical expert able to provide senior-level analysis, review, and support for any engineering work done by the company. Has a vested interest in the success of the firm as an owner in the corporation. Serves as the senior technical advisor and able to provide technical support and oversight. Can perform any and all duties for all labor categories.
